Here Father Gonzales, of the Mission, took the greatest pains to discover some of the Indians who had been taken from those islands, eighteen years before, but not one of them could be found, and what becameof them, is a mystery unto this day. }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs16 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs15\fs16\insrsid5911984 {\*\atrfend 415666248}{\*\atnid SS}{\*\atnauthor Sara Schwebel}\chatn {\*\annotation{\*\atnref 415666248}{\*\atndate -953705478}\ltrpar \pard\plain \ltrpar
